{"tha-ap457:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap457:0.2":"Jagatidayakavagga ","tha-ap457:0.3":"Akkamanadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap457:1.1":"“Kakusandhassa munino, ","tha-ap457:1.2":"brahmanassa vusimato; ","tha-ap457:1.3":"Divaviharam vajato, ","tha-ap457:1.4":"akkamanamadasaham. ","tha-ap457:2.1":"Imasmimyeva kappamhi, ","tha-ap457:2.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap457:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap457:2.4":"akkamanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap457:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap457:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap457:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap457:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap457:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap457:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap457:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap457:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap457:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap457:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma akkamanadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap457:7.1":"Akkamanadayakattherassapadanam pancamam. "}